Text.string: Hey there!
Greetings!
Hiya!
Howdy!
You here for me?
Nice day, huh?
Hot as hell and twice as muggy, ain't it?
Evenin'.
Nice night for a dance in the dark.
Don't mess with The Pact. That's a warning for ya.
I ain't no mud worshipper, if that's what yer thinkin'.
Have you met Murl? He's a great mentor. So learned.
I need to find some live chickens for... reasons. Know where I can get a few?
I'll never worship at the feet of those Calypso bastards. The Pact forever!
Give me some mushrooms, a roaring fire, and a pint of blood of an innocent—and I'll get a party STARTED!
My dreams have been full of dark tidings lately... but I'm sure it's probably nothin'.
I'm only a witch of the fourth aleph. Still got a long ways to go.
I've had to skip the last few stitch-'n'-bitch sessions on account of everythin' that's goin' on lately.
You've got a powerful aura, Vault Hunter.
Have you seen my tome? Dang it, I'm always losing my tome!
I know magic ain't really real, but it's fun to pretend. Besides, the Pact ain't a cult or anything... I don't think. Would I know? I'd probably know.
I'm savin' up for a Double-Double brand cauldron. With that lifetime three witches guarantee!
A cauldron's a handy thing. You can make potions and explosives and soup. Multi-purpose!
Those COV don't understand what kind of powers they're messing with on Eden-6! Their time will come...
I can't feel the leylines on this ship.
I feel so disconnected from the land up here.
I will say, the cosmic energies in space are very powerful.
Sanctuary is no place for occult rituals. Which is really too bad.
The darkness of space goes well with the darkness of my soul... heh, just kiddin'. I'm actually a very happy person.
[yawns]
[yawns]
[yawns]
[yawns] Boy, I'm tired!
[yawns]
[yawns] Y'all wore me out.
May the Pact protect ya!
Be sure to follow the dark word!
I banish thee! Sorry, it's a habit...
Now we are bound...
May darkness consume you!
KEEP AN EYE OUT FOR MY EYELINER PENCIL!
Beware the killing moon!
Heed the shadow's warning.
And so you are initiated!
I will protect you!
Come, night splinter. Embrace me!
I miss my Pact-mates.
I will not stray from the path, I will not stray from the path.
[witch cackle]||—Hoo, still got it!
I sense someone intruding on my thoughts.
I will try to control the Vault Hunter now. Do as I command. Yes... yes... it's working!
Has anyone seen a vial full of grog eyes? Anyone?
Now, where'd I leave my tarot deck?
I wonder if Mordecai is single.
Just gotta keep studying.
Got my next aleph test coming up.
Oh, you mighty crushing bone, praise your name, protect my home.
The invocation! It must be... no, not here. Not now.
Wayward sisters, hand in hand, posters of the sea and land, innocent blood will soak the sand.
Let me consult... the book... No! Not yet.
Go Pact it up!
I'm gunnin' for ya!
You're invited to the aleph!
I'm easily excited!
Told ya I'm a happy person!
Whatever's happenin', I love it!
You are worthy of love!
Your feelings are valid!
It's okay to love yourself. In private.
[burps]
[burp] Somethin' in that spell book wasn't right.
[burp] No more cauldrons before bedtime.
You got a friend in me!
How y'all doin'?
Ain't seen you in a month of Sundays!
I'll always be watchin'! Pact-style!
Y'all better bring back my potion bowls, now!
Mind writin' me a letter of recommendation?
